{"tid":2426114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好累","createTime":"2021-02-27T20:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T21:37:38.000Z","uid":175919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab74293f6787e7567f23213e1e5b57edd80bd42","tid":2426114,"uid":175919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T20:54:52.000Z","msg":"之前俾我篤爆幾次佢意圖出軌之後 <br />\n佢話唔會再做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然近排啲行為真係好左好多 覺得佢真係有改善到嘅<br />\n但我心一直時忘記唔到之前嘅嘢<br />\n每次一星期唔到又會哎交<br />\n好似有被害妄想症咁 我都唔知佢幾時又會再次出軌<br />\n佢一做錯少少野我就會好敏感就會發脾氣<br />\n心力交瘁<br />\n究竟應該繼續咁樣定係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ba16dec819591c4f3e789f49af6616c5eca3f2","tid":2426114,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T21:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f8a45e4c6b55d2e14ac729615b07735734500e","tid":2426114,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T21:37:38.000Z","msg":"哈 又一pair準備分手 開心～"}]}